comments.body: Thanks for the ID! I was thinking Dragonhunter because of its reputation for taking down other dragonflies and butterflies. I have now added a duplicate of this observation under Mourning Cloak.

@jhiebert  - great photos, do you mind entering any one of them separately as a Mourning Cloak observation?  you can actually copy (duplicate in the "Edit" drop-down list) the observation, and just change the species.

results.description: A Dragonhunter preying upon a Mourning Cloak, which it took out of the sky above our campsite.
